{"tid":656530,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁 詠 琪 現 身 童 裝 店 幫 楊 采 妮 挑 選 童 裝","createTime":"2018-05-07T10:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T10:27:06.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"755b302f82d76e95083c48eb5c7b7493b55ade0c","tid":656530,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:27:06.000Z","msg":"楊采妮（Charlie）今日幫好姊妹梁詠琪（GiGi）老公Sergio，免費宣傳童裝店，Charlie表示跟GiGi夫婦不講錢，認真唔話得。活動結束後，Charlie在店內選購童裝，相信是挑選給她的14個月大的孖仔，昨晚才舉行完演唱會的GiGi，突然在店內現身，並與老公一齊幫眼，替Charlie揀童裝，期間GiGi不時給予Charile意見，傾得好開心呢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180506/s00007/1a935ff0fc32a380babec46e2119d4f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180506%2Fs00007%2F1a935ff0fc32a380babec46e2119d4f1.jpg&h=813db34f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}